ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectLA CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE LEMÈQUE CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval for LA CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE LEMÈQUE, in New Brunswick (a) to change its name to the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DES ILES LAMÈQUE ET MISCOU; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to the Lamèque and Miscou Islands.
